@startuml stats-mixin
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class DescriptiveStatisticsMixin <<abstract>> {
  +annotate_extrema(x, y)
  +annotate_statistics(x, y)
  +plot_extrema(x_min, y_min, x_max, y_max) <<abstract>>
  +plot_statistics(y) <<abstract>>
}

class MatplotlibBackend

MatplotlibBackend --|> DescriptiveStatisticsMixin

note right of DescriptiveStatisticsMixin
plot_extrema(...) and plot_statistics(...)
are ABSTRACT.
Every backend that uses this mixin
MUST IMPLEMENT BOTH.

--

annotate_statistics:
- calls plot_statistics(y)
- optionally calls annotate_extrema(x, y)
end note

@enduml
